:: Question 3:2:1 Aggressive {"position":"1750,2275","size":"100,100"}
<<silently>>
<<set $aggressive += 1>>
<<set $DamienOpinion -= 1>>
<<endsilently>>"What?" Damien looks... concerned.

"I just mean... well, we’re dead, so this crisis obviously isn’t a natural disaster or anything. It’s interpersonal," you say, making very direct, very intentional eye-contact with damien. "And if you’re so concerned about making sure everyone here is a ‘good fit,’ then fine. Whoever is causing the problem can leave."

Damien looks stunned. Several times he opens his mouth to speak, but closes it again, unsure what to say. Frustrated, you finally speak up.

"Look, this can’t be an unexpected answer. That’s basically what you’re doing here. If you don’t fit in, you’re kicked to the curb."

"I... see."

[[Continue. |Explore 2 Choice]]
