:: Explore 2 Choice {"position":"2200,2525","size":"100,100"}
"Alright," Damien says before standing, phasing through the arm of the chair and the table. He moves to the side so that he's not currently inside any furniture and looks down at you, still seated. "Thank you for your time and your candor."

"Are–" you start, eyes widening. Was that the interview? Is he about to ask me to leave?

"We are not done just yet, if that is what you were wondering," He says, raising a hand to cut off your questioning, a knowing smile on his face. "I simply need to confer with the other residents for a moment. I will ask that you stay here, and not go wandering the halls or seeking out any of the other ghosts. I will not be long, and you are welcome to wait here in the meantime."

Damien turns with purpose and strides away, not so much as sparing you a glance or giving you the time to respond. He ascends the massive staircase you saw when you entered and is gone from sight in only a few moments.

You sit in the open room, surrounded by the oppressive silence of the dead house, and ponder your options. It may not be in your best interest to do what your interviewer expressly asked you not to do, but since he left in such a hurry, you technically never agreed not to explore a little.

[[Go explore.|Explore 2:1]]
[[Stay and wait.|Explore 2 Wait]]
<img src="images/damien1.png" width="512" height="512">


