<img src="images/intro1.jpeg" width="512" height="512">


:: Explore 2:2:1:3 Nervous {"position":"2875,2700","size":"100,100"}
<<silently>>
<<set $LydiaOpinion -= 1>>
<<endsilently>>You watch her for nearly a minute before she finally notices you. When she does, she catches sight of you from the corner of her eye, holding you in her piercing, green gaze. You cringe. This would probably have been less awkward if you had just gone up and spoken to her.

She turns to you, rolling her shoulders., "You just gonna stand there or are you gonna help?" she asks.

You swallow, finding it harder to speak. "I don't know how." She nods.

She walks over to you, looking you up and down. "Lydia," she says. "And you must be the one Damien's got doing that interview."

[["That's right."|Explore 2:2:1:4]]
<img src="images/intro1.jpeg" width="512" height="512">


