<<silently>>
<<set $LydiaOpinion += 1>>
<<endsilently>>She misses the nail as the hammer sails directly through her thumb, hissing through her teeth in surprise. You watch as she jerks her hand out of the way before realizing that the hammer can't harm her. Then she turns to you.

"How do you do that?" you ask, smiling to relieve the tension of having obviously startled her.

The woman eyes you up and down, a piercing and scrutinizing green gaze, before shrugging and saying, "It's not so hard, once you figure out how."

