"They are obviously a biased source." Damine says, rolling his eyes.

"Exactly," Lydia replies. "They're affected by this, they should get a say. so, new ghost, let's hear it."
<<else>><<set $seenLydia = true>><<set $seenJunia = true>>"Why not?!" You hear a shout in an unfamiliar voice. You round the corner and see three figures in a room with an open door. The first is Damien, tall but hardly imposing in comparison with the person standing to his left. The person to his left is an older woman, with pale skin and grey hair in a long braid down her back. She's wearing a pair of overalls and a t-shirt, as well as a very worn pair of work gloves. The argument they're having seems quite heated. The woman in particular looks very angry.

