:: Lydia Question 1:1 {"position":"2525,4125","size":"100,100"}
<<silently>>
<<set $LydiaOpinion += 1>>
<<endsilently>>"Hmm," Lydia verbalizes as she props her head on her hands, deep in thought. "It's partly about being here. Or somewhere like here. I couldn't move things until I lived here, and it wasn't just about learning how. It's hard to practice and get better at something when you aren't sure where you'll be laying your head each day. You need that stability first, then moving things is easier."

[[Continue.|Interview End 2]]
